  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates that YY1 acts as a transcription factor that directly binds to and activates JAK2, leading to JAK2/STAT3 pathway activation and subsequent EMT in gastric cancer progression.",
    "The research provides evidence for YY1 as both a biomarker for poor prognosis and a potential therapeutic target in H. pylori-associated gastric cancer."
